    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This specimen features a recently serviced double-VANOS system, ensuring optimal cam phasing and linear power delivery across the rev range. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to address factory structural weaknesses, maintaining rigid suspension geometry. It utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential for superior torque vectoring. The dampers remain responsive, and the braking system features refreshed lines for consistent pedal modulation. While the paintwork shows light road-rash typical of a performance vehicle, the drivetrain is robust and free of parasitic loss. A true enthusiast's build with the mechanical integrity to match its pedigree.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
